name: be your own enginge - black/white
description:

name: Hipster Juice - seafoam
description:
12"x12" original art digital print

this 12x12 print has a 1" thick boarder, is printed with ultrachrome K3 archival ink, using bright white 80# archival enhanced matte paper.

this lil' diddy is almost good enough to drink! who doesn't like an ice cold PBR, the golden goodness, that keeps the hipsters lookin hip while quenching the thirst of those on a show-string budget.

the common size makes this print easily and inexpensively framed. a pre-cut mat frame from ikea fits this print perfectly.

Bicycles and PBR rock! 

©2009 briana auel. this image is proprietary to briana auel and is not transferable with sale of print.

name: hearts & minds mini - slate
description:
12x12 original art digital print

this 12x12 print has a .5" thick boarder, is printed with ultrachrome K3 archival ink, using bright white 80# archival enhanced matte paper.

hearts & minds is a mini version of my print that was part of the 2009 ARTCRANK poster show in minneapolis. the title has significant meaning, and the copy on the poster reads: "in loving memories of fallen riders." minneapolis is a bike heavy community, and this poster was made in honor and in memory of a few friends who were hit and run victims. the hearts on the heads also signify the importance of wearing helmets while riding.

the common size makes this print easily and inexpensively framed. **frame in picture is not included, sale is for print only.

bike love forever!

©2009 briana auel. this image is proprietary to briana auel and is not transferable with sale of print.

name: Mister Pot(ato) Head
description:
12 x 12 digital print

signed, limited edition of 30.

printed using ultrachrome K3 archival ink on an epson pro 3800 digital printer. 80# archival matte bright white paper.

this print is 12"x12" with a 1" white border. the colors are soft and complementary while mister pot(ato) head proudly displays a PBR in one hand and an F-U to society in the other. a cute little heart, that is incorporated on every BHSC print, resides subtly in the left corner.

easily and inexpensively framed with a pre-cut mat frame from ikea.
